{"tid":2016893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十一個月了。","createTime":"2020-05-14T17:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T18:33:50.000Z","uid":120729,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aab9fe11c6da8d19994b70e3cfaf22ebcc8760cf","tid":2016893,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:51:07.000Z","msg":"點解會過得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似上個月先發生嘅事<br />\n當日應承過要代佢行落去，無論幾灰心都好，唔好放棄。<br />\n我相信所有在天之靈嘅手足如果仲喺到嘅話，佢哋都唔會放棄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnwzMR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnwzMR5.jpg&h=b4911d33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbBjXYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbBjXYM.jpg&h=334fe9ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45908c17ea7fb911b867b463b8c56b5ce490e415","tid":2016893,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"53fc7323c00062e9f81337d20cbf49f865f541d0","tid":2016893,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"真係話咁快就一年...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9521be4251acd55548af44b3127cf784c83530e3","tid":2016893,"uid":120729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdf5b97266adc0f10eb2f5be9e047156db1d037","tid":2